headline: Stock market today: Dow, S&P 500, Nasdaq rally as Fed cuts interest rates by 25 basis points
summary: US stocks tipped mostly into the green on Wednesday after the Federal Reserve cut rates by 25 basis points in its final policy decision of the year.

headline: Fed Rate Decision, Adobe and Oracle Earnings: Still to Come This Week

Here's what to expect: Today   Earnings: Adobe, Oracle (?more on the AI trade), Synopsys, Vail Resorts   Economic data: Monthly federal data on deficits/surpluses and delayed quarterly employment cost index   Fed decision: The central bank is expected to cut rates by 0.
